We are glad to present you a new version of the Diary! In this version we have done: Add up to 5 images to one diary entry Editing records has become even more convenient and simple Improved application speed Fixed bugs

We are very glad to present you completely new design settings for your Personal Diary! Meet the amazing night mode. Three ways to set up night mode: System Adaptive and Schedule. Set your favorite themes separately for day and night mode. Now the interaction with the diary has become even more enjoyable thanks to the tactile response to your actions. Choose the color of your diary!
